OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy in the evening with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain. Staying cloudy
OL,8,Fovernight with further rain, heavy and
OL,9,Fperhaps thundery at times. Gentle
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloud and occasionally heavy,
OL,13,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing.
OL,14,FThen sunny spells and scattered
OL,15,Fshowers, occasionally heavy with a
OL,16,Fchance of thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
