OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and bright Monday morning with
OL,7,Fsunny spells, cloud and outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain later. Mostly cloudy Tuesday and
OL,9,FWednesday with rain or showers, heavy
OL,10,Fand thundery at times.
